07:24.800 --> 07:27.680
They say you're never more than
three feet from a local historian.

07:27.680 --> 07:28.880
Or is that rats?

07:28.880 --> 07:30.440
DEBORAH AND MANDY LAUGH

07:31.560 --> 07:33.560
Er, so, erm, are you up for it?

07:33.560 --> 07:35.760
Yeah. Just let me put
