relatives to help you out.

08:23.080 --> 08:27.040
And I found this in the local paper
from the time.

08:28.160 --> 08:30.920
So February the 8th, 1902.

08:30.920 --> 08:33.600
Miss Lizzie Haworth
has been taken to court

08:33.600 --> 08:35.480
