would only take a few minutes.

08:51.240 --> 08:54.000
Harder work, though,
with less fingers, so.

08:55.760 --> 08:57.200
And cut.

08:57.200 --> 09:00.160
Thanks, Jeffery, that was wonderful.
Exactly what we're looking for.

09:00.160 --> 09:03.160
Don't you want to see some
of the old factory records?

09:03.160 --> 09:05.800
Er, no, that's great. We've got
